# ============================================================================
# Notes for Collaborators
# ============================================================================
# If you need to track large files:
# 1. Install Git LFS: git lfs install
# 2. Track file type: git lfs track "*.pth"
# 3. Commit .gitattributes: git add .gitattributes
#
# To check what's being ignored:
# git status --ignored
#
# To force-add an ignored file:
# git add -f filename